##  To check the list of PYTHON available : uv python list
##  For create a venv with specific P ver : uv venv env --python cpython-3.11.15-windows-x86_64-none
##  Install the requiremnet for the env   : uv pip install -r requirements.txt
##  Set path to specific folder where Git : $env:Path += ";C:\Program Files\Git\bin;C:\Program Files\Git\cmd"

